name: Beach Stripe Cushion
description:
This exclusive cushion design features a timeless colour combination that's punctuated with classic stripes and backed in a gorgeous linen look fabric. Its coastal shades and classic pattern have been hand picked by Nest Design’s Interior Stylist, Emma Blomfield, and digitally brought to life on white fabric by an Australian textile printer.

With a crisp and contemporary energy, it complements a beachside interior, and shakes up a modern living and bedroom space. Its durable design works hand-in-hand with your everyday décor.

45 x 45cm piped cushion cover. 

Designed and made in Australia.

Cushion cover only. Feather insert additional.
